# Unit 12

## 1. Reflection and Position

This unit required critical engagement  with future trends in security and risk management through a seminar debate. I identified the convergence of cybersecurity and supply chain risk as the most influential trend based on increasing digital interdependence and reliance on cloud based systems.

Contributing to the discussion strengthened my ability to evaluate competing viewpoints and justify my position using evidence. It also reinforced the importance of forward looking risk management, where emerging threats must be anticipated rather than reacted to. Overall this unit enhanced my ability to think strategically about how risk management will evolve in complex, digitally intergrated environments.
